FBIS4-37742 "drnes122_o_94002" FBIS-NES-94-122 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 SYRIA Al-Asad Cables Iran's President, Denounces Bombing Al-Asad Cables Iran's President, Denounces Bombing JN2306171194 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1515 GMT 23 Jun 94 JN2306171194 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] President Hafiz al-Asad has sent a cable to Akbar Hashemi-Rafsanjani, president of the Islamic Republic of Iran, expressing his condolences over the victims of the criminal incident in the city of Mashhad. The following is the text of the cable: We have been extremely pained by the falling of victims as a result of the criminal incident which occurred in the holy city of Mashhad. We strongly denounce this incident and express to your excellency and to the families of the victims our heartfelt condolences. We pray to God Almighty to grant the injured speedy recovery.
